records.name: Vaali Maldives Island Escapes & Dive

descriptions.direction: Located in Felidhoo, Vaali Maldives Island Escapes & Dive is on the beach. While the natural beauty of Aarah Island and Alimathaa can be enjoyed by anyone, those looking for an activity can check out Felidhoo Harbor. Looking to get your feet wet? Scuba diving and boat tours adventures can be found near the property.
descriptions.general: Facing the seafront, Vaali Maldives Island Escapes & Dive offers 3-star accommodation in Felidhoo and has a private beach area, open-air bath and garden. The property features sea and garden views. The accommodation offers free WiFi throughout the property, as well as a terrace and a family-friendly restaurant.
descriptions.other: Please share your flight details with the property at least 3 days before your arrival to secure your seat(s) for the transfer.
